{"tid":480001,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"施永青：我最憎就是聖誕！... 我X你老母！","createTime":"2017-11-25T16:26:35.000Z","updateTime":"2017-11-27T14:48:53.000Z","uid":2054,"like":29,"dislike":1,"uniUserReply":7,"replies":[{"pid":"034ac94f072250954a42444df780c6e261d76cdd","tid":480001,"uid":2054,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-11-25T16:26:35.000Z","msg":"聖誕前各公司互送聖誕卡、果籃，聊表心意，不過中原地產創辦人施永青對「聖誕」就有Hard Feeling，《壹週刊》報道，施永青一聽到「聖誕」無名火起：「我最憎就是聖誕！」，細個因為屋企窮，無錢買聖誕卡買，所以他將人哋送畀佢張聖誕卡，改咗自己個名送畀人，點知同學將件事唱通街，超慘！仲話，「我已經同佢反左面架喇！」<br />\n<br />\n依家施永青財力雄厚，想送幾多果籃塞住人哋把口都得啦！佢話雖然收大把果籃，但一個都唔會送出去，仲好激動咁話，「你咪唔好同我做生意囉，笨！我X你老母」嚇到個記者打咗個突，童年的影響之大，真係唔講得笑！"},{"pid":"0b09606727786dc5f899c1c7c72079e30c1a4982","tid":480001,"uid":61280,"like":7,"dislike":1,"score":6,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-11-25T16:32:40.000Z","msg":"<span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\"><strong><span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\"><span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\"><strong><span style=\"color: red;\">自<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n卑<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n變<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n自<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n瀆<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n！<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/z.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> </span></strong></span></span></strong></span>"},{"pid":"6af07ac40cfaec3db3ccab5b4d17d361acc3b75b","tid":480001,"uid":31452,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-11-25T16:46:11.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/10.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/10.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"5294c433397034414049fc0379fd06c2c5cdfbd8","tid":480001,"uid":81183,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-11-25T16:47:55.000Z","msg":"篇文睇左好多年<br />\n究竟係真定假<img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/37.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"e9dd2d3bf928ee84fbdc8c5fe94c782b29c2b7fe","tid":480001,"uid":3773,"like":4,"dislike":0,"score":4,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-11-25T20:45:32.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>篇文睇左好多年<br />\n究竟係真定假<img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/37.png\" cl